       <div class="od mainContent">
         <h2 class="text-center classname">新闻动态</h2>
       <div class="od mainContent">
       <h1 class="aTitle">祝贺电力钢冒自动打磨机床研制成功</h1>
       <h2 class="articleTime">添加时间:2019-12-26&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>阅读次数:&nbsp;&nbsp;<script src="/index.php?c=article&a=hits&id=197" type="text/javascript"></script></span></h2>
       <div class="introduction nmt">
         <h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; height: 35px; line-height: 35px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; word-break: keep-all; text-indent: 6px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); text-align: center;">博恩科自动化电力钢冒自动打磨机床<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></h1><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/20191226/1577368352992560.jpg" title="3285971803.jpg" alt="3285971803.jpg" width="529" height="274" style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 目前大多企业都遭受着招工难、用工贵的困扰，抛光打磨行业尤其严重，并且职业病多发；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/20191226/1577368353123405.jpg" title="3384041151.jpg" alt="3384041151.jpg" style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;">电力金具-电力钢冒生产企业目前主要的打磨方式仍然依赖人工，其中有少部分企业开始进行“机器人换人”升级改造；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">然而，关节机械手在抛光打磨方面的应用，对减速机性能的要求还是比较高的。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">对于五金抛光打磨行业，电力金具、电力钢冒打磨来说，产品附加值不是特别高，数量大、产品型号标准，在打磨方面的应用设备，专用抛光打磨机床的性价比要高于机器人；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/20191226/1577368353787176.jpg" title="3470651714.jpg" alt="3470651714.jpg" style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">以上也是博恩科自动化研发电力钢冒自动打磨设备的背景，对此设备感兴趣的朋友，欢迎详细了解，前来考察；海滨古城，长寿之乡--莱州，欢迎您的到来。</p><p><br/></p>         <div class="od articlePages">
         <div class="text-right"><a href="/article/198.html">上一页:&nbsp;自动打磨机的用途与适用行业！</a></div>         <div class="text-right"><a href="/article/196.html">下一页:&nbsp;如何对自动数控抛光打磨机日常保养</a></div>         <div class="text-right"><a href="/article/type/12-1.html">返回列表</a></div>
         </div>
       </div>
   </div>
       </div>
     </div>
       
   
